@5500 = ~Thy bravery has not passed without notice, child of Bhaal. I applaud thee for thy valiancy. Thou chose a harder path and prevailed. 'Tis no small task to defeat the Prince of Demons.~
@5501 = ~Helm the All-Seeing has deemed thy courage worthy of reward. Take this gift. It contains powerful wards blessed by The Watcher himself. They will protect thee in trials to come.~
@5502= ~Thy companions shall be compensated too, for such is the will of Helm. Accept the offerings, Child of Bhaal, go forth and be safe.~